text: Laraesima ecuadorensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1974. It is known from Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Laraesima ecuadorensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1974
